                  chuckleDay
chukleDay app is all about joke based on Actor Chuck Norris. 
For regular users, it will show 5 jokes about him. 
It will generate 5 random jokes about him each time user refreshes the page. 
For registered user there will be an extra feature of save and delete. 
where he/she will be able save the jokes in Favorite or  delete them them from their favorite folders.




Big Thanks: 
  The Internet Chuck Norris Database www.ICNDb.com for making api freely available.


Also thanks to: Daniel, Hadas, Mohamed, Natty,Sam and Valeria for help
